                                            Ringkasan Kolektif
                                        </h2>
                                        <div className="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
                                            <div className="p-4 bg-surface rounded-2xl border border-border shadow-sm">
                                                <p className="text-[10px] font-black text-text-secondary uppercase">Jumlah Atlet</p>
